textContent:
Let love eclipse the fear

If you have not done the work to set the boundaries your ego will find work and busyness bc it quiets your fear 

Have you done the work to allow yourself to accept the gift that this is 

My personal growth has come with me liking to dabble experiment and prototype. I like to be a constant learner, prototype and do. I don't like to be still. I like to be creating. And the moment I'm not creating I go fuck this. 

My boundary line with my family is being able to cook, shop, clean, read, be at their big moments in life ... And let go
